DepositBN254Test
├── when the deposit keys do not pass the proof of possession check
│   └── it reverts
└── when the deposit keys pass the proof of possession check
    ├── when proof of possession has been seen before
    │   ├── when the original key holder is still active
    │   │   └── it reverts
    │   └── when the original key holder is not active
    │       └── it adds the keys
    └── when proof of possession has not been seen before
        └── it adds the keys
